<div id="pf4488" class="pf w4d h2fe" data-page-no="4488"><div class="pc pc4488 w4d h2fe"><div class="t m1dc x92 h5 y2f16 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">LESSON 12 September 16-22 </div><div class="t m74f x26 h5 y4b ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;Therefore whosoever heareth </div><div class="t m2a2 x27 h5 ya9 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">these sayings of mine, and doeth </div><div class="t m100 x27 h5 yda4 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">them, I will liken him unto a wise man, </div><div class="t mcd3 x27 h5 y593 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">which built his house upon a rock: and </div><div class="t mae3 x27 h5 y193 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the rain descended, and the floods </div><div class="t m735 x27 h5 y14d ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">came, and the winds blew, and beat </div><div class="t maf2 x27 h5 y559 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">upon that house; and it fell not: for it </div><div class="t m64d x27 h5 y69f ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">was founded upon a rock&quot; (Matt. 7:24, </div><div class="t m3f x27 h5 y2b5 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">25). </div><div class="t m7ca x26 h35 y662 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">These last two lessons are of vital </div><div class="t m192 x27 h35 ydc3 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">importance. Just a theoretical </div><div class="t m286 x27 h35 y1ba ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">knowledge of the tremendous events </div><div class="t m978 x27 h35 y2fe ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">of this last hour of earth&apos;s history will </div><div class="t mf52 x27 h35 yb6 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">not be enough to carry us safely </div><div class="t m1175 x27 h35 y17c ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">through the time of trouble, to meet </div><div class="t ma74 x27 h35 yfe4 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Jesus with great joy, and to be able to </div><div class="t m553 x27 h35 y24c ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">enter with Him through the pearly </div><div class="t m223 x27 h35 y15 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">gates. </div><div class="t m98a x18 h35 y5f ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">We need a preparation. The rain will </div><div class="t me97 x27 h35 y605 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">descend, the winds will blow, the </div><div class="t m6b4 x27 h35 y11 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">flood will come. Our house should be </div><div class="t m854 x27 h35 ye3 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">built upon the Rock of Ages. We need </div><div class="t m2c8 x27 h35 ybf ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">to build right now a relationship with </div><div class="t ma3e x27 h35 y5ff ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Jesus that will enable us to receive the </div><div class="t m4f0 x11 h35 y10d ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">seal of the living God, the fullness of </div><div class="t mb9 x11 h35 y391 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the Spirit. We must reach a stage of </div><div class="t m12b x11 h35 y87e ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">victory over sin and of righteousness </div><div class="t m4db x11 h35 y1b53 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">imparted by Christ that makes us able </div><div class="t m894 x11 h35 y96f ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">to stand without a mediator during the </div><div class="t ma75 x11 h35 y425 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">time of trouble and be received at last </div><div class="t mb24 x11 h35 y1e0 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">into our heavenly home. </div><div class="t m100c x18 h35 y2b ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;My brethren, do you realize that </div><div class="t m72b x11 h35 y78 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">your own salvation, as well as the </div><div class="t m212 x11 h35 y2f ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">destiny of other souls, depends upon </div><div class="t mad9 x11 h35 y7e ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the preparation you now make for the </div><div class="t m1d2 x11 h35 y81 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">trial before us? Have you that intensity </div><div class="t m33d x11 h35 y10b2 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">of zeal, that piety and devotion, which </div><div class="t m8cb x11 h35 y279 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">will enable you to stand when </div><div class="t m65c x11 h35 y5e8 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">opposition shall be brought against </div><div class="t mdff x11 h35 y629 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">you? ... The time that so many are now </div><div class="t m888 x11 h35 y3f ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">allowing to go to waste should be  </div><div class="t m6de x70 h35 ycbd ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">devoted to the charge that God has </div><div class="t m888 x70 h35 y8df ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">given us of preparing for the </div><div class="t m6d4 x70 h35 y60c ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">approaching </div><div class="t m3ad x62 h35 y313 ff5 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">crisis.&quot;—Testimonies, </div><div class="t m41c x70 h35 y9e0 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">vol. 5, pp. 716, 717. </div><div class="t m3a0 xab h35 y387 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;I saw that God&apos;s people are on the </div><div class="t m6d2 x70 h35 y6de ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">enchanted ground, and that some </div><div class="t m6d4 x70 h35 ya3a ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">have lost nearly all sense of the </div><div class="t m3f4 x70 h35 yd7 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">shortness of time and the worth of the </div><div class="t m1351 x70 h35 y2db ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">sou I </div><div class="t m6ae xa5 h35 y2db ff5 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">.&quot;—Early Writings, </div><div class="t m1d2 xca h35 y75b ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">p. 120. </div><div class="t m862 xab h35 y8b ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;The people need to be aroused in </div><div class="t m750 x70 h35 yac4 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">regard to the dangers of the present </div><div class="t m1af x70 h35 y6ec ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">time. The watchmen are </div><div class="t m7ae x70 h35 ya5e ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">asleep.&quot;—Testimonies, vol. 5, p. 715. </div><div class="t mbb3 x8 h35 y2fe ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Our willingness to obey should </div><div class="t m845 x70 h35 y70f ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">cause us to take whatever steps are </div><div class="t ma69 x70 h35 y626 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">necessary to be really ready. In these </div><div class="t m594 x70 h35 yfe4 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">final lessons we plan to study the </div><div class="t mb12 x70 h35 y9ab ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">specific factors of this spiritual </div><div class="t m9f7 x70 h35 y15 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">preparation. </div><div class="t m4d6 x70 h5 ye1c ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">DAILY HIGHLIGHTS </div><div class="t m23f x70 h5 y11 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">1. </div><div class="t m3d3 x7b h5 y43c ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Time With God </div><div class="t m4ff x22 h5 y9d1 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Mark 6:30, 31) </div><div class="t m558 x70 h5 yc0 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">2. </div><div class="t m114 x7b h5 yc0 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Alone With God </div><div class="t m284 x22 h5 y589 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Mark 1:35) </div><div class="t mb7 x70 h5 y10d ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">3. </div><div class="t m223 x7b h5 y10d ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Daily Dying </div><div class="t m358 x22 h5 y391 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(1 Cor. 15:31) </div><div class="t m1ce x56 h5 yc56 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">4. </div><div class="t m3ef x22 h5 y87e ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Study of the Scripture </div><div class="t m467 x22 h5 y1b53 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(John 6:63) </div><div class="t m8a8 x56 h5 y96f ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">5. </div><div class="t m3a2 x22 h5 yfdd ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Prayer and Communion </div><div class="t ma3b x22 h5 y425 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Luke 18:1) </div><div class="t m2ef x56 h5 y324 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">6. </div><div class="t maf6 x22 h5 y324 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Christ in You </div><div class="t m385 x22 h5 y2b ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Col. 1:27) </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
